							li Simple UI for adding and managing cities. Search or browse 10,000+ cities by name.
							li <strong>Widgets</strong> available in many sizes and styles, including Lock Screen, Home Screen, and Today widgets.
							li Put clocks on your bedside with beautiful digital clock widgets designed especially for <strong>StandBy mode</strong> (requires iOS 17).
